Invocation Name: cloud dummy
des:
Cloud Computing Dummy teaches you useful cloud computing Acronyms, definitions and tips with fun quizzes. A fun and fresh game to help boost your cloud computing vocabulary and learn new stuff every day! Get ahead in cloud computing with this fun game!

THOUSANDS OF CLOUD COMPUTING MULTI-CHOICE AND TRUE OR FALSE QUESTIONS! 
Enjoy thousands of fun, family-friendly questions to keep all ages entertained for hours. 
You're guaranteed to learn new computing stuffs everyday! Get your brain boosted, test your knowledge of cloud computing, learn new amazing things you didn't know in the internet and computing world! 


Please email Tweet @clouddummyskill with your feedback and suggestions.
